  "description": "As part of our Savour The Summer menu, this easy breezy French-inspired chicken dish features pan-fried chicken, golden potatoes and green beans, all tumbled together with fragrant tarragon, toasted pistachios and capers. This dish begs to be eaten al fresco with a chilled glass of white wine...",
